<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.4">
<l>tāṅkaruñ ciṉattu vaṉtāḷ taṭakkaimā maruppu vāṅki</l>
<l>pūṅkurun tocittup puḷvāy piḷanteru taṭartta ventai</l>
<l>māṅkaṉi nukarnta manti vantuvaṇ ṭiriya vāḻait</l>
<l>tīṅkaṉi nukarum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, having removed the tusk of an elephant with a thick trunk</l>
<l rend="indent">and strong legs, whose rage was difficult to bear,</l>
<l>Having broken the flowering kuruntu tree [and] split the bird’s mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">controlled the bull,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where a she-monkey,</l>
<l rend="indent">which had relished mango fruit,</l>
<l>Comes, so the bees take flight, and relishes the sweet fruit</l>
<l rend="indent">of the banana [tree].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
